metadata.name: Flight
metadata.description:
Camera: Fujifilm X-Pro2
Lens: Fujinon XF 27mm/f2.8
Dimensions: 5121x3414

All photos in the "Monochrome Nature" collection were shot on either a Fujifilm X-Pro2 with modern and vintage lenses (23, 27, 35 and 50mm), or a Yashica FX-3 analog camera with a Helios 58mm/f2 lens.
